data.description: PRICED TO SELL - Presenting an exquisitely designed two-story residence in Lantana Village! Lovely façade displays a 2-car garage and stone accents. Check out the inviting hallway leading to the spacious great room featuring wood-look flooring in all the right places, an entertainment niche, and sliding glass doors that open to the back patio. Modern kitchen is a cook's delight, equipped with recessed lighting, SS appliances, granite counters, tile backsplash and a walk-in pantry. In the bright main retreat, you'll find a private bathroom with dual sinks and a walk-in closet. Lastly, the large backyard offers a covered patio ideal for unwinding after an exhausting day!
